name: peace friendship gum
description:
hello everyone!
Happy to share my work with you! These bunnies were made to cheer you up, to make you look at them, how ridiculous and funny they are. Don't forget to check them out sometimes and read their tablets ;)
Creativity is a great meditative process, creative and light, i wish you all do it ♡

*the physical painting will go as a gift for my grandmother
